Package ca.keefer.sanemethod.LevelBuilder

Class Summary
LevelShapeBuilder This class allows me to draw paths/polygons overlaying individual elements of a tile map, and save the points of the polygon as a text representation of an array of floats in an xml file which contains information on the shape, and the location of the element within the context of the tile map.
MapShape This class contains a Shape, and holds a variety of additional information pertinent to the association of this shape with an element from a TiledMap.
TileSheetLoadDialog Extends the JDialog to get the string reference and integere cellwidth and cellheight of a tileSheet
XMLShapeOutput  
XMLShapePullParser This class implements an xml pull parser to fetch a specific tile shape definition whenever a tile position on a tilesheet with a matching xml file is passed to this class object.
